<div class="job-details mt-20">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">

            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="back-page">
                    <a href="<%- locals.base %>employer/search-candidates/<%- locale %>">

                        <img src="<%- locals.base %>img/svg/arrow-left.svg" alt="arrow-left" class="svg">
                        go back</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-sm-12 mb-30">
                <div class="job-details-card">
                    <div class="job-details-card__top flex-wrap">
                        <div class="job-item__image">
                            <a href="#">
                                <div class="generateAvatar job-item__image-img img-fluid"><%-
                                        simulation.candidate_id.name.split(' ').slice(0, 2).map(word => word.charAt(0)).join('') %></div>
                            </a>
                            <div class="job-item__title">
                                <a href="jobDetails.html">
                                    <h3 class="card-title"><%- simulation.candidate_id.name %></h3>
                                </a>
                                <span><%- simulation.candidate_id.current_location %></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                    <div class="job-details-card__middle">
                        <h4>Simulation Description</h4>
                        <p>There are have a many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available, but the randomised
                            words which don' t look even slightly believable. If you are going to sdsss embarrassing
                                        hidden in the middle of text. All the Lorem Ipsum generators on the Internet
                                        tend to repeat predefined chunks as necessary, making which don't first true
                                        generator on the Internet.</p>
                                        <h4>Simulations Data</h4>
                                        <div class="tab-content" id="v-pills-tabContent">
                                            <div class="tab-pane fade active show" id="v-pills-home" role="tabpanel"
                                                aria-labelledby="v-pills-home-tab">
                                                <!-- Edit Profile -->

                                                <div class="application-faqs">
                                                    <div class="panel-group" id="accordion" role="tablist"
                                                        aria-multiselectable="true">
                                                        <!-- panel 1 -->
                                                        <% for (let i=1; i <=simulation['completed_milestones']; i++) {
                                                            %>
                                                            <div class="panel">
                                                                <div class="panel-heading" role="tab"
                                                                    id="heading<%-i%>">
                                                                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                                                                        <a data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                                                            data-parent="#accordion"
                                                                            href="#collapse<%-i%>" aria-expanded="true">
                                                                            Miilestone <%- i %> details
                                                                        </a>
                                                                    </h3>

                                                                </div>
                                                                <div id="collapse<%-i%>"
                                                                    class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tabpanel"
                                                                    aria-labelledby="heading<%-i%>">
                                                                    <div class="panel-body">
                                                                        <div class="form-group row mb-25">
                                                                            <div
                                                                                class="col-sm-3 d-flex aling-items-center">
                                                                                <label for="inputName"
                                                                                    class=" col-form-label color-dark fs-14 fw-500 align-center">Milestone
                                                                                    <%- i %> Expectation</label>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                            <div class="col-sm-9 pt-1">
                                                                                <%- simulation["milestone" + parseInt(i)
                                                                                    + "_expectation" ] %>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                        <div class="form-group row mb-25">
                                                                            <div
                                                                                class="col-sm-3 d-flex aling-items-center">
                                                                                <label for="inputName"
                                                                                    class=" col-form-label color-dark fs-14 fw-500 align-center">Milestone
                                                                                    <%- i %> Skills</label>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                            <div class="col-sm-9 pt-1">
                                                                                <%- simulation["milestone" + parseInt(i)
                                                                                    + "_skill" ] %>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                        <div class="form-group row mb-25">
                                                                            <div
                                                                                class="col-sm-3 d-flex aling-items-center">
                                                                                <label for="inputName"
                                                                                    class=" col-form-label color-dark fs-14 fw-500 align-center">Milestone
                                                                                    <%- i %> Rating</label>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                            <div class="col-sm-9 pt-1">
                                                                                <%- simulation["milestone" + parseInt(i)
                                                                                    + "_skill_rating" ] %>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>

                                                                        <div class="form-group row mb-25">
                                                                            <div
                                                                                class="col-sm-3 d-flex aling-items-center">
                                                                                <label for="inputName"
                                                                                    class=" col-form-label color-dark fs-14 fw-500 align-center">Milestone
                                                                                    <%- i %> Submisstion</label>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                            <div class="col-sm-9 pt-1">
                                                                                <% if(simulation["milestone" +
                                                                                    parseInt(i) + "_submission_type"
                                                                                    ]==='file' ){ %>
                                                                                    <%- "<a download href='/simulations/"
                                                                                        +simulation.candidate_id._id+"/"+simulation['milestone'
                                                                                        + parseInt(i) + '_submission' ]
                                                                                        + "' class='mr-2 btn btn-info btn-xs btn-squared'>Download Attachment</a>"
                                                                                        %>

                                                                                        <% }else{ %>
                                                                                            <%- simulation["milestone" +
                                                                                                parseInt(i)
                                                                                                + "_submission" ] %>
                                                                                                <% } %>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </div>
                                                                </div>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <%}%>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 mb-30">
                        <div class="job-details-widget">
                            <h4>Information</h4>
                            <div class="job-item__content d-inline-flex flex-column">
                                <div class="job-type">
                                    <h6>Name:</h6>
                                    <span><%- simulation.candidate_id.name %></span>
                                    <input type="hidden" id="candidate_id" value="<%- simulation.candidate_id._id%>">
                                    <input type="hidden" id="simulation_id" value="<%- simulation._id%>">
                                    <input type="hidden" id="whole_number" value="<%- simulation.candidate_id.phone%>">
                                </div>
                                <div class="job-type">
                                    <h6>Email:</h6>
                                    <span><%- simulation.candidate_id.email %></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="job-type">
                                    <h6>Phone:</h6>
                                    <span id="maskNumber"><%- maskNumber(simulation.candidate_id.phone) %></span>
                                    <span style="margin-left: 15px">
                                        <butto onclick="handleButtonClick('view_contact')" id="maskNumberBtn"
                                            class="mr-2 btn btn-info btn-xs btn-squared btn-block ">View
                                            Number</button>
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="job-type">
                                    <h6>Job Title:</h6>
                                    <span><%- simulation.candidate_id.job_title %></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="job-type">
                                    <h6>Current Location:</h6>
                                    <span><%- simulation.candidate_id.current_location %></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="job-type">
                                    <h6>Expected Salary:</h6>
                                    <span>&#8377;<%- simulation.candidate_id.monthly_expected_salary %></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="job-type">
                                    <h6>Resume:</h6>
                                    <span><a download href="/resumes/<%- simulation.candidate_id.resume %>"><button
                                                onclick="handleButtonClick('resume_download')" id="maskNumberBtn"
                                                class="mr-2 btn btn-info btn-xs btn-squared btn-block ">Download</button></a></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <script>
            function maskNumber(number) {
                const numberStr = number.toString();
                const mask = numberStr.slice(0, -4).replace(/\d/g, ' *'); return mask + numberStr.slice(-4);
            } </script>